name: Brighton seafront
description:
There is something about the Brighton coast that I can't help but think about. I stayed in this hotel room with a seaview in 2019 and decided to move there the next month. After that, I had to leave Brighton and Hove, but I still miss it every day.

Digital illustration made in 2021. Collector will own a token of an artwork. JPG 2160 × 2700 px
